			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Rāhui and the Art of Marine Conservation</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">In French Polynesia, an ancient practice puts everyone in charge of protecting the sea.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/tiare-tuuhia/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Tiare Tuuhia</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
