																																															<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/tiare-tuuhia/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_bottom" >
											<div class="container col3 ">
												<div class="col span2"><p>Tiare Tuuhia is an independent print and audio journalist based in French Polynesia. She writes about the environment, travel, culture, and Indigenous issues. Her work has appeared in outlets such as <em>National Geographic</em>, <em>The Guardian</em>, and Rest of World and has been aired on ABC Radio Australia.</p></div>
